# 🐍 Snake Game

A classic Snake Game built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. Use arrow keys or on-screen buttons to control the snake, eat food, and grow longer. Avoid hitting walls or yourself!

## 🚀 Live Demo

👉 [Play the Game Here](https://your-username.github.io/snake-game/)  
(Replace with your actual deployed link)

## 🎮 How to Play

- Use the **arrow keys** on your keyboard (or on-screen buttons if on mobile):
  - ⬆️ Up Arrow → Move Up
  - ⬇️ Down Arrow → Move Down
  - ⬅️ Left Arrow → Move Left
  - ➡️ Right Arrow → Move Right
- Click **Play** to start the game.
- Eat food (🍎) to grow your snake.
- Avoid colliding with walls or yourself.

